data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN OPTION AVAILABLE NOW! Ask for Details!!  Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 5-bedrm, 2.5-bth offers everything you need for a comfortable and luxurious living. The living room is very expansive to entertain in! The beautiful kitchen that has all stainless-steel appliances, gas range, large pantry and stunning quartz countertops. The primary bdrm is a true oasis w great space, including a 5 pieces ensuite and a walk-in closet! Enjoy your backyard with an extended paver patio or stay cool this summer with your CENTRAL AC!!! Convenience is key, and this home delivers. Situated in a desirable location, just a stone's throw away from shopping and easily access to the highway, ferry and shipyards, making commuting a breeze.
